        "subject": "LU-3645 osc: wait for objects until recovery complete",
        "message": "LU-3645 osc: wait for objects until recovery complete\n\nin osc, if there is no more precreated object and the osc is\nin recovery, or -EAGAIN is returned, or recoverable errors are\nreturned from osc_create_interpret, then continue waiting until\nthe recovery is completed or other errors are returned.\n\nSigned-off-by: Hongchao Zhang <hongchao.zhang@intel.com>\nChange-Id: Iaf2fc8a60407874d6c3f97432a7f03809d9eca93\n"
      },
